    <item>
      <title>阿达尼开始讨论兴登堡以来首个美元债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-06/adani-starts-talks-for-first-dollar-bond-sale-since-hindenburg</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度亿万富翁高塔姆·阿达尼 (Gautam Adani) 的集团正在商谈通过美元债券筹集约 5 亿美元的资金，这是自去年美国卖空者的一份报告引发人们对该集团借款再融资能力的担忧以来，该集团首次在海外发行债券。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-06/adani-starts-talks-for-first-dollar-bond-sale-since-hindenburg</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 05:29:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着救援押注的增加，习近平将与监管机构讨论中国股市</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-06/xi-set-to-discuss-china-stock-market-with-financial-regulators</link>
      <description><![CDATA[人们越来越期待中国政府采取更有力的措施来结束股市暴跌，监管机构计划最早于周二向习近平主席通报市场情况。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-06/xi-set-to-discuss-china-stock-market-with-financial-regulators</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 04:17:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳洲联储将利率维持在 12 年高位，暗示加息门槛更高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-06/rba-keeps-rate-at-12-year-high-signals-tightening-may-be-done</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚央行将利率维持在 12 年高位，并暗示仍有可能进一步收紧政策，与全球央行一起抵制近期宽松政策的预期，并推高货币和债券收益率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-06/rba-keeps-rate-at-12-year-high-signals-tightening-may-be-done</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 03:35:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
